0.2.1 (2014-01-23):

  Minor maintenance release.

  * Build system fixes
  * No functional changes


0.2 (2013-05-28):

  Minor improvements release with major code changes.

  * Code refactoring and cleanup
  * Build for Nemo 3.x by default
  * Drop GConf dependency for Nemo 3.x
  * New translations: de, ru


0.1.1 (2011-08-18):

  Minor improvements of 0.1 release.

  * Support for GTK 3.x (and thus Nemo 3.x)
  * Minor UI cleanup of the progress dialog


0.1 (2011-05-15):

  Initial release.
